title: Brady Quinn on NFL Coaching Rumors, Divisional Round (Football 1/10)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn to break down the Kliff Kingsbury hire in Arizona (1:00), Bruce Arians landing in Tampa (21:00), Matt LeFleur's hiring in Green Bay (28:45), which direction the Miami Dolphins might go (40:00) and preview the Divisional Round playoff games (45:00).
